{
  "page": "House Polander",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Polander</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Polander.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Polander.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Polander.svg/250px-House_Polander.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Polander.svg/375px-House_Polander.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Polander.svg/500px-House_Polander.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nPer bend sinister, three red hearts and three gold lions on white, a broken sword silver on purple<br /><i>(Per bend sinister white and purpure, three lions or each clutching a heart gules, a broken sword silver)</i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Polander</b> is a house in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>. According to semi-canon sources they blazon their arms with per bend sinister, three red hearts and three <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lions</a> on white, a broken <a href=\"/index.php/Sword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sword\">sword</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> on purple.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Their words and seat are unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Polander_at_the_end_of_third_century\">House Polander at the end of third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Polander&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Polander at the end of third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Polanders during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>no member has appeared yet.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Polander&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The name \"Polander\" is a reference to fantasy and sci-fi writer <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poul_Anderson\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Poul Anderson\">Poul Anderson</a>. The house's arms are a reference to his novels <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Three_Hearts_and_Three_Lions\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Three Hearts and Three Lions\"><i>Three Hearts and Three Lions</i></a> and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Broken_Sword\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:The Broken Sword\"><i>The Broken Sword</i></a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Polander&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/10/\">Houses from an unknown region</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:HousesUnknown\" title=\"Template:HousesUnknown\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:HousesUnknown&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:HousesUnknown (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:HousesUnknown&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nHouses of Unknown Regions</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Lordly Houses</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Belgrave\" title=\"House Belgrave\">Belgrave</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/